data.description:
Welcome 1260 Peacock Dr, nestled in the picturesque landscape of Oconee County! This charming residence boasts three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a bonus room above the garage, offering endless possibilities for customization.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen, dining area, and living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones. The generously sized kitchen offers ample counter space, and abundant storage options.
Beyond the main living area, discover the allure of an unfinished basement, ready to be transformed into a personalized retreat or additional living space tailored to your unique needs. Step outside onto the back porch and savor the serene beauty of the large, private backyard, providing a peaceful oasis for outdoor gatherings or quiet moments of relaxation.
Conveniently located less than 4 miles from North Oconee High School, this home offers easy access to education and community amenities. With proximity to Hwy 78 and Hwy 53, commuting to nearby attractions and destinations is a breeze, ensuring both convenience and connectivity for residents.
Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home in the heart of Oconee County. Schedule your showing today and let your dreams of homeownership come to life!
